org.codice.ddf.admin.application.service.impl

Interface ApplicationServiceBeanMBean

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationServiceBean

    public interface ApplicationServiceBeanMBean
    Interface for the Application Service MBean. Allows exposing the application service out via a JMX MBean interface.
